trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] sequence, see chapter 2 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that contains the default printing options for the sequence; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if no print ticket exists for the document.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> ，其中包含序列中的預設列印選項或<xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>，如果文件不有任何的 print ticket。
